                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My opinion, 
<br />
 
<br />
It is bad business to assert ones needs based on a comparison to another class. 
<br />
 
<br />
You point is valid, but if I were a developer I would toss it out as simply Yet Another Class vs Class Rant. 
<br />
 
<br />
One may want to push the issue based on the Charm Duration (aka break) vs DPS, should be higher than a pet/animation that can not break charm. 
<br />
 
<br />
I mean no offense, I am simply pointing out one does not need to involve a class comparison to make this point.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Morpheus to Neo, "Remember -- all I am offering is the truth, nothing more." 
<br />

